28 (3d) Quarterhorse. – A horse that is registered with the American Quarter Horse
29 Association.
30 (3e) Satellite facility. – A facility, controlled by a legacy track operator, that is
31 located within a 20-mile radius of the legacy track affiliated with the legacy
32 track operator.
